Rotarran<i> Combat Log,</i>

598
00:33:53,949 --> 00:33:57,410
<i>the 53rd day in the year</i>
<i>of Kahless 999.</i>

599
00:33:57,410 --> 00:33:59,454
<i>We have reached</i>
<i>the Cardassian border</i>

600
00:33:59,454 --> 00:34:02,624
<i>and begun our search</i>
<i>for the</i> B'Moth.

601
00:34:02,624 --> 00:34:05,210
Helm... keep us at least

602
00:34:05,210 --> 00:34:07,754
five million<i> kellicams</i>
from the border.

603
00:34:07,754 --> 00:34:09,130
Understood.

604
00:34:09,130 --> 00:34:11,049
