I think I've
got something.

605
00:34:11,049 --> 00:34:12,968
It's hard to make out
through all the interference,

606
00:34:12,968 --> 00:34:15,012
but the thermal signature
looks like a ship.

607
00:34:15,012 --> 00:34:17,514
It's bearing direct
to starboard

608
00:34:17,514 --> 00:34:20,099
at an elevation
of 25 degrees.

609
00:34:20,099 --> 00:34:21,560
It's coming into
visual range.

610
00:34:21,560 --> 00:34:23,353
On screen.

611
00:34:33,446 --> 00:34:36,408
TAVANA:
The<i> B'Moth.</i>
Confirmed.

612
00:34:36,408 --> 00:34:38,410
Helm, lay in a course
to bring us alongside.

613
00:34:38,410 --> 00:34:41,705
Bridge to Medical Ward.
Prepare to receive casualties.

614
00:34:41,705 --> 00:34:44,041
Assemble an armed boarding party
in Transporter Room 1.

615
00:34:44,041 --> 00:34:46,292
Make a complete search
of all the habitable areas--

616
00:34:46,292 --> 00:34:47,460
Hold.

617
00:34:47,460 --> 00:34:48,921
Commander Dax,

618
00:34:48,921 --> 00:34:51,214
