625
00:35:09,315 --> 00:35:11,693
they do not care what side
of the border we are on.

626
00:35:11,693 --> 00:35:13,361
They will simply attack.

627
00:35:13,361 --> 00:35:15,321
I have explicit orders
from the High Council

628
00:35:15,321 --> 00:35:17,198
not to enter
Cardassian territory.

629
00:35:17,198 --> 00:35:18,825
I am certain the High Council

630
00:35:18,825 --> 00:35:20,744
will not object
under these circumstances.

631
00:35:20,744 --> 00:35:22,412
There are still survivors
aboard the<i> B'Moth.</i>

632
00:35:22,412 --> 00:35:24,372
We do not know that.

633
00:35:24,372 --> 00:35:26,708
All that we know is there is
an automated distress call.

634
00:35:26,708 --> 00:35:30,003
They could all be dead by now.
And if they are not?

635
00:35:31,588 --> 00:35:34,800
Then there is nothing
we can do for them.

636
00:35:34,800 --> 00:35:39,512
