740
00:42:15,908 --> 00:42:17,618
waiting for us at the airlock

741
00:42:17,618 --> 00:42:20,538
so that we can celebrate
the first victory

742
00:42:20,538 --> 00:42:24,667
of the<i> Rotarran</i>
over the Jem'Hadar!

743
00:42:24,667 --> 00:42:26,794
(<i> Klingons laughing</i>
<i>lustily</i> )

744
00:42:29,297 --> 00:42:31,383
(<i> laughing and yelling</i> )

745
00:42:37,263 --> 00:42:38,806
Worf.

746
00:42:38,806 --> 00:42:40,475
General.

747
00:42:40,475 --> 00:42:42,601
The High Council
has issued a commendation

748
00:42:42,601 --> 00:42:45,813
for the entire crew
of the<i> Rotarran.</i>

749
00:42:45,813 --> 00:42:48,900
It would seem
that you were right.

750
00:42:48,900 --> 00:42:51,403
They view the destruction
of a Jem'Hadar ship

751
00:42:51,403 --> 00:42:54,531
and the rescue of 35 warriors
as ample justification

752
00:42:54,531 --> 00:42:56,866
for crossing
the Cardassian border.

753
00:42:56,866 --> 00:43:01,204
Your... actions
on the<i> Rotarran--</i>

754
00:43:01,204 --> 00:43:03,540
at the time,
I thought they were disloyal

755
00:43:03,540 --> 00:43:06,042
but I have come
to realize

756
00:43:06,042 --> 00:43:08,294
that your intention
was to remind me of my duty

757
00:43:08,294 --> 00:43:10,338
as a soldier of the Empire
and as a warrior.

758
00:43:10,338 --> 00:43:12,340
For that, I am grateful.

759
00:43:12,340 --> 00:43:14,217
You did the same
for me once.

760
00:43:14,217 --> 00:43:15,843
Worf...

761
00:43:17,178 --> 00:43:19,931
on the Bridge,
during the fight,

762
00:43:19,931 --> 00:43:22,141
when you dropped
your guard,

763
00:43:22,141 --> 00:43:25,061
how did you know
I would not kill you?

764
00:43:29,315 --> 00:43:31,192
I did not know.

765
00:43:31,192 --> 00:43:34,653
(<i> chuckling</i> )

766
00:43:34,653 --> 00:43:36,281
I see you're still wearing

767
00:43:36,281 --> 00:43:38,074
the crest
of the House of Mogh.

768
00:43:41,286 --> 00:43:42,995
Yes.

769
00:43:42,995 --> 00:43:46,541
Jadzia calls it
a... sentimental gesture.

770
00:43:46,541 --> 00:43:52,589
Ah. Perhaps you would consider
replacing sentiment with...

771
00:43:52,589 --> 00:43:55,508
the symbol
of a new beginning.

772
00:43:58,344 --> 00:44:01,556
The House of Martok

773
00:44:01,556 --> 00:44:03,808
would be honored

774
00:44:03,808 --> 00:44:06,978
to welcome the son of Mogh
into our family

775
00:44:06,978 --> 00:44:08,271
as a warrior...

776
00:44:09,730 --> 00:44:11,107
and as a brother.

777
00:44:28,040 --> 00:44:30,418
<i>Qapla'!</i>
<i>Qapla'!</i>
